name: Tedn Dahai
Lore: 'Male Bith musician. Member in good standing of the Intergalactic Federation of Musicians. Plays the Fanfar in Figrin D''an''s band. Once worked for the Empire as a scout.',
Text: 'For each other musician at same site, during any control phase you may use 1 Force to choose one opponent''s alien present. That alien cannot utilize its game text for remainder of that turn.',
